
SDK接口:
  BluetoothAdapter.isEnabled()
  BluetoothAdapter.startDiscovery()

使能:
    Intent enableBtIntent = new Intent(BluetoothAdapter.ACTION_REQUEST_ENABLE);
    startActivityForResult(enableBtIntent, REQUEST_ENABLE_BT);

    RequestPermissionActivity处理Intent
    然后经过RequestPermissionHelperActivity弹出dialog
    确认后调用LocalBluetoothAdapter.enable()

    systemui使能时会调用另外一个接口:
    LocalBluetoothAdapter.setBluetoothEnabled()



BluetoothManagerService实现IBluetoothManager

AdapterService.AdapterServiceBinder实现IBluetooth
  static {
      System.load("/system/lib/libbluetooth_jni.so");
      classInitNative();
  }

